{"id":192,"date":"2024-03-23T16:31:04","date_gmt":"2024-03-23T16:31:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/?page_id=192"},"modified":"2024-04-03T14:15:17","modified_gmt":"2024-04-03T14:15:17","slug":"slam","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/slam\/","title":{"rendered":"SLAM"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full has-custom-border is-style-default wp-duotone-unset-1\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_003711536.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-49\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-radius:100px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_003711536.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_003711536-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-1 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"border-width:12px;border-radius:100px\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">SLAM signifie \u00ab\u2009Solutions Logicielles et Applications M\u00e9tier\u2009\u00bb.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">L\u2019option&nbsp;<strong>SLAM&nbsp;<\/strong>forme l\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve \u00e0 d\u00e9velopper, \u00e0 adapter et \u00e0 maintenir des solutions applicatives.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">L\u2019option SLAM est destin\u00e9e aux \u00e9tudiants qui s\u2019orientent vers les m\u00e9tiers li\u00e9s \u00e0 la conception et la maintenance de programmes applicatifs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Cette option permettra de veiller au maintien et au bon fonctionnement des services informatiques. Vous d\u00e9velopperez et adapterez des solutions logici